 968   // (X+ 2) >s X       --> X <s (MAXSINT-(2-1))       --> X <s 126
 969   // (X+MAXSINT) >s X  --> X <s (MAXSINT-(MAXSINT-1)) --> X <s 1
 970   // (X+MINSINT) >s X  --> X <s (MAXSINT-(MINSINT-1)) --> X <s -2
 971   // (X+ -2) >s X      --> X <s (MAXSINT-(-2-1))      --> X <s -126
 972   // (X+ -1) >s X      --> X <s (MAXSINT-(-1-1))      --> X == -128
